thank you

> Hey, the patch looks good to me, but I cannot reproduce the bug, so
 > I cannot verify if the patch fixes the issue. Could you give some
 > more information on how to reproduce the bug? Either here or in

 > 
 > thank you

Thanks for your review. 
The way to reproduce this bug:
The way to reproduce this bug.

1. Create a nova instance which boot from volume or snapshot.
2. Do snapshot of the nova instance, this will generate a new image with id xxx.
3. Use command 'glance image-download --file 134.raw xxx' to download the image.
4. Error occurred.

The size of the image with this type is zero(you can see it from image show), so the image you download is 0.
This patch only fix the 500 error, and I think the zero size should be another issue or maybe it should be a new feature to download image from volume boot instance's snapshot.
